solved slow shutdown:
mark controlpanel->bootvis->empty choice on list, then press save.
run botvis->trace(menu)->optimize system
reboot

The problem with slow computer in solidworks soled temporarily.
move dragbar for hardware graphic acceleration

Hey guys. Seems my slow shutdowns have been eliminated. Not sure what was causing the problem... It was something slowly saving to disk before shutdown. Till I tweaked the system and this stopped occurring I had to shutdown / restart the pc from the task manager window. No harm done though, Ive got an old 1 ghz cpu which could have explained the issue as well.
Best of luck with your installs and such.
